text: Peter Eržen (born 13 December 1941) is a Slovenian ski jumper. He competed at the 1964 Winter Olympics and the 1968 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:Slovenian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Yugoslavia Category:Ski jumpers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:Ski jumpers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Kranj
